text: Shariff Aguak is a municipality in the province of Maguindanao del Sur, Philippines. According to the 2020 census, 33,982 people lived there. Shariff Aguak was founded on September 11, 1963 as Maganoy. In 1996, the town's name was changed from Maganoy to Shariff Aguak. Category:Settlements in the Philippines Category:Maguindanao del Sur
title: Shariff Aguak
